          "CRITIQUE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "** BY AUTHOR ** Application of method with 5He-particle",
                " energy fixed at 15.4 MeV, as reported by of Cheifetz,",
                " to data of Loveland for 252Cf, and of D'hondt et al.",
                " and Caitucoli et al. for 235U(n,f), where the alpha",
                " spectra extend to ~0.1MeV, leads to ternary 5He yields",
                " much larger than the 4He data and to very different",
                " FWHM fit for the two He isotopes.  This is at variance",
                " with the experimental observation that, for ternary",
                " particles of the same charge, widths of energy",
                " distributions are independent of mass."
              ]
            }
          ],
